Is there an elegant way to calculate the mean of a variable within a cutoff of another variable y in dplyr?
cutoff <- 20
x <- rnorm(100)
y <- round(runif(100,1,100))
val <- c()

for(i in 1:length(x)){
  val[i] <- mean(x[which(y[i]-y <= cutoff & y[i] >= y )])
}
